"Desain CADSTAR berisi varian yang tidak memiliki padanan KiCad. Hanya varian "
"master ('%s') yang dimuat."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:396
msgid ""
"The CADSTAR design contains grouped items which has no KiCad equivalent. Any "
"grouped items have been ungrouped."
msgstr ""
"Desain CADSTAR berisi item yang dikelompokkan yang tidak memiliki padanan "
"KiCad. Semua item yang dikelompokkan telah dibubarkan."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:403
#: pcbnew/pcb_io/cadstar/cadstar_pcb_archive_loader.cpp:163
msgid ""
"The CADSTAR design contains re-use blocks which has no KiCad equivalent. The "
"re-use block information has been discarded during the import."
msgstr ""
"Desain CADSTAR berisi blok penggunaan ulang yang tidak memiliki padanan "
"KiCad. Informasi blok penggunaan ulang telah dibuang selama impor."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:517
msgid ""
"CADSTAR fonts are different to the ones in KiCad. This will likely result in "
"alignment issues. Please review the imported text elements carefully and "
"correct manually if required."
msgstr ""
"Font CADSTAR berbeda dari yang ada di KiCad. Ini kemungkinan akan "
"mengakibatkan masalah perataan. Harap tinjau elemen teks yang diimpor dengan "
"cermat dan perbaiki secara manual jika diperlukan."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:522
#: pcbnew/pcb_io/cadstar/cadstar_pcb_archive_loader.cpp:172
msgid ""
"The CADSTAR design has been imported successfully.\n"
"Please review the import errors and warnings (if any)."
msgstr ""
"Desain CADSTAR telah berhasil diimpor.\n"
"Harap tinjau kesalahan dan peringatan impor (jika ada)."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:541
#: pcbnew/pcb_io/cadstar/cadstar_pcb_archive_loader.cpp:76
#, c-format
msgid ""
"The design is too large and cannot be imported into KiCad. \n"
"Please reduce the maximum design size in CADSTAR by navigating to: \n"
"Design Tab -> Properties -> Design Options -> Maximum Design Size. \n"
"Current Design size: %.2f, %.2f millimeters. \n"
"Maximum permitted design size: %.2f, %.2f millimeters.\n"
msgstr ""
"Desain terlalu besar dan tidak dapat diimpor ke KiCad. \n"
"Kurangi ukuran desain maksimum di CADSTAR dengan navigasi ke: \n"
"Tab Desain -> Properti -> Opsi Desain -> Ukuran Desain Maksimum. \n"
"Ukuran Desain saat ini: %.2f, %.2f milimeter. \n"
"Ukuran desain maksimum yang diizinkan: %.2f, %.2f milimeter.\n"

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:602
msgid ""
"The selected file is a CADSTAR symbol library. It does not contain a "
"schematic design so cannot be imported/opened in this way."
msgstr ""
"Berkas yang dipilih adalah pustaka simbol CADSTAR. Tidak mengandung desain "
"skematik sehingga tidak dapat diimpor/dibuka dengan cara ini."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:607
msgid "The CADSTAR schematic might be corrupt: there is no root sheet."
msgstr "Skematik CADSTAR mungkin rusak: tidak ada lembar akar."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:681
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Part definition '%s' references symbol '%s' (alternate '%s') which could not "
"be found in the symbol library. The part has not been loaded into the KiCad "
"library."
msgstr ""
"Definisi bagian '%s' mereferensikan simbol '%s' (alternatif '%s') yang tidak "
"dapat ditemukan di pustaka simbol. Bagian tidak dimuat ke pustaka KiCad."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:704
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Part definition '%s' has an incomplete definition (no symbol definitions are "
"associated with it). The part has not been loaded into the KiCad library."
msgstr ""
"Definisi bagian '%s' memiliki definisi yang tidak lengkap (tidak ada "
"definisi simbol yang terkait). Bagian tidak dimuat ke pustaka KiCad."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:751
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Symbol '%s' references part '%s' which could not be found in the library. "
"The symbol was not loaded"
msgstr ""
"Simbol '%s' mereferensikan bagian '%s' yang tidak dapat ditemukan di "
"pustaka. Simbol tidak dimuat"

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:845
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Symbol ID '%s' references library symbol '%s' which could not be found in "
"the library. Did you export all items of the design?"
msgstr ""
"ID Simbol '%s' mereferensikan simbol pustaka '%s' yang tidak dapat ditemukan "
"di pustaka. Apakah Anda mengekspor semua item desain?"

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:857
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Symbol ID '%s' is a signal reference or global signal but it has too many "
"pins. The expected number of pins is 1 but %d were found."
msgstr ""
"ID Simbol '%s' adalah referensi sinyal atau sinyal global tetapi memiliki "
"terlalu banyak pin. Jumlah pin yang diharapkan adalah 1 tetapi ditemukan %d."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:1000
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Symbol ID '%s' is of an unknown type. It is neither a symbol or a net "
"power / symbol. The symbol was not loaded."
msgstr ""
"ID Simbol '%s' memiliki tipe yang tidak diketahui. Ini bukan simbol maupun "
"net daya / simbol. Simbol tidak dimuat."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:1016
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Symbol '%s' is scaled in the original CADSTAR schematic but this is not "
"supported in KiCad. When the symbol is reloaded from the library, it will "
"revert to the original 1:1 scale."
msgstr ""
"Simbol '%s' diskalakan dalam skematik CADSTAR asli tetapi ini tidak didukung "
"di KiCad. Saat simbol dimuat ulang dari pustaka, akan kembali ke skala asli "
"1:1."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:1484
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Documentation Symbol '%s' refers to symbol definition ID '%s' which does not "
"exist in the library. The symbol was not loaded."
msgstr ""
"Simbol Dokumentasi '%s' merujuk ke ID definisi simbol '%s' yang tidak ada di "
"pustaka. Simbol tidak dimuat."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:1593
msgid "Text Variables could not be set as there is no project attached."
msgstr ""
"Variabel Teks tidak dapat diatur karena tidak ada proyek yang terlampir."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:2120
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Symbol '%s' is rotated by an angle of %.1f degrees in the original CADSTAR "
"design but KiCad only supports rotation angles multiples of 90 degrees. The "
"connecting wires will need manual fixing."
msgstr ""
"Simbol '%s' diputar sebesar %.1f derajat dalam desain CADSTAR asli tetapi "
"KiCad hanya mendukung sudut rotasi kelipatan 90 derajat. Kabel penghubung "
"perlu diperbaiki secara manual."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:2134
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Symbol '%s' references sheet ID '%s' which does not exist in the design. The "
"symbol was not loaded."
msgstr ""
"Simbol '%s' mereferensikan ID lembar '%s' yang tidak ada dalam desain. "
"Simbol tidak dimuat."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:2270
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Net %s references unknown net element %s. The net was not properly loaded "
"and may require manual fixing."
msgstr ""
"Net %s mereferensikan elemen net yang tidak diketahui %s. Net tidak dimuat "
"dengan benar dan mungkin perlu perbaikan manual."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:2533
#, c-format
msgid ""
"The block ID %s (Block name: '%s') is drawn on sheet '%s' but is not linked "
"to another sheet in the design. KiCad requires all sheet symbols to be "
"associated to a sheet, so the block was not loaded."
msgstr ""
"ID blok %s (Nama Blok: '%s') digambar di lembar '%s' tetapi tidak tertaut ke "
"lembar lain dalam desain. KiCad mengharuskan semua simbol lembar dikaitkan "
"dengan lembar, sehingga blok tidak dimuat."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:2558
#, c-format
msgid ""
"The CADSTAR schematic might be corrupt: Block %s references a child sheet "
"but has no Figure defined."
msgstr ""
"Skematik CADSTAR mungkin rusak: Blok %s mereferensikan lembar anak tetapi "
"tidak memiliki Gambar yang didefinisikan."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/sch_io_cadstar_archive.cpp:227
msgid ""
"Path to the CADSTAR schematic archive (*.csa) file related to this CADSTAR "
"parts library. If none specified it is assumed to be 'symbol.csa' in the "
"same folder."
msgstr ""
"Jalur ke berkas arsip skematik CADSTAR (*.csa) terkait dengan pustaka bagian "
"CADSTAR ini. Jika tidak ditentukan, diasumsikan 'symbol.csa' di direktori "
"yang sama."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/sch_io_cadstar_archive.cpp:232
msgid ""
"Name of the footprint library related to the symbols in this library. You "
