msgid ""
"Materials with a high comparative tracking index (CTI) are better at "
"providing isolation.\n"
"\n"
"Material group I: 600 <= CTI\n"
"Material group II: 400 <= CTI < 600\n"
"Material group IIIa: 175 <= CTI < 400\n"
"Material group IIIb: 100 <= CTI < 175"
msgstr ""
"Material dengan indeks pelacakan komparatif (CTI) tinggi lebih baik dalam "
"memberikan isolasi.\n"
"\n"
"Kelompok material I: 600 <= CTI\n"
"Kelompok material II: 400 <= CTI < 600\n"
"Kelompok material IIIa: 175 <= CTI < 400\n"
"Kelompok material IIIb: 100 <= CTI < 175"

