msgid "Fix all segments on click"
msgstr "Tetapkan semua segmen saat klik"

#: pcbnew/dialogs/dialog_pns_settings_base.cpp:113
msgid ""
"When enabled, all track segments will be fixed in place up to the cursor "
"location.  When disabled, the last segment (closest to the cursor) will "
"remain free and follow the cursor."
msgstr ""
"Jika diaktifkan, semua segmen trek akan dikunci di tempat hingga lokasi "
"kursor. Jika dinonaktifkan, segmen terakhir (terdekat dengan kursor) akan "
"tetap bebas dan mengikuti kursor."

