#: resources/linux/metainfo/org.kicad.kicad.metainfo.xml.in:50
msgid ""
"KiCad is a free and open-source electronics design automation (EDA) suite. "
"It features schematic capture, integrated circuit simulation, printed "
"circuit board (PCB) layout, 3D rendering, and plotting/data export to "
"numerous formats. KiCad also includes a high-quality component library "
"featuring thousands of symbols, footprints, and 3D models. KiCad has minimal "
"system requirements and runs on Linux, Windows, and macOS."
msgstr ""
"KiCad adalah suite otomasi desain elektronik (EDA) gratis dan sumber "
"terbuka. Fiturnya mencakup penangkapan skematik, simulasi sirkuit terpadu, "
"tata letak papan sirkuit cetak (PCB), rendering 3D, dan ekspor plot/data ke "
"berbagai format. KiCad juga menyertakan pustaka komponen berkualitas tinggi "
"dengan ribuan simbol, footprint, dan model 3D. KiCad memiliki persyaratan "
"sistem minimal dan berjalan di Linux, Windows, dan macOS."

